CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in the Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 13, 1954, pg. 12 reads: " More Queen Contestants - Another group of Pittsburgh teen-agers who are clamoring to wear the crown of Hill City Queen includes, left to right,...Katheryn Harris...Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Two frames: Portrait of young woman wearing neck scarf and light colored long sleeved blouse, posed in front of light colored background in Harris Studio; Portrait of Katheryn Harris wearing light colored sheer dot and line patterned blouse and gingham jumper, posed in front of light colored background in Harris Studio for Hill City Teen Queen contest
